data.description:
Stop the car! This beautiful home has been renovated to make 100 year old history come back to life. The layout fits anysize family and has complete, amazing main floor living, with so much more additional living space upstairs!
This home is filled with charm, located in the in historic Englewood Arts District.  Prior renovators updates include- restored hardwood floors throughout the main level, washer/dryer on main level, new appliances and kitchen cabinets, new electrical (including a new panel), new plumbing throughout ( including new water and sewer lines), and second floor primary suite with its own HVAC. Exterior updates included a new driveway/patio, exterior painting, new gutters, and windows that have been historically restored.
Come get a new feel with old charm, its waiting for you to WELCOME you HOME!
